  <programme start="20260308083700 +0100" stop="20260308092000 +0100" channel="Stingray Classica">
    <title lang="pl">Documentary 2017</title>
    <desc lang="pl">TivoliVredenburg, Utrecht, The Netherlands. This short documentary follows the participants of the 11th International Franz Liszt Piano Competition, held in TivoliVredenburg, Utrecht, in 2017. The competition actively presents, develops, and promotes piano talents from around the world. In doing so, it has become one of the prominent gateways to the international professional classical music scene for young musicians. The International Franz Liszt Piano Competition was founded in 1986 in the Netherlands and has since built a reputation as one of the world's most prestigious piano competitions.</desc>
